window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Triumphing in the Guild Tournament, despite outside interferences, Nate has gained entry to the Etruan Royal University.</p> <p>With his System Challenge over and a path to learning more about magic and the System he exists within, he is hoping for a quiet year or two during which he can grow. That growth however is drawing attention to him and unknown enemies lurk in the shadows, waiting for the opportunity to pounce.</p> <p>Can Nate rise to the challenge, or will he finally meet his end at the hands of those that covet his gifts?</p>"; 
